Question.Subject: my internet explorer wont work?
Question.Content:
When i click on internet explorer the page comes up and then it says "internet explorer cannot display the web page" i can get onto Aol but not onto internet explorer.
Can anyone help me?
Question.ChosenAnswer: Try these methods to resolve the problem. 1. Clear cached data in Internet Explorer 2. Reset security settings for Internet Explorer 3. Run Internet Explorer in "No Add-Ons" mode 4. Reset Internet Explorer 5. Use the Manage Add-ons tool to determine which add-on is causing the issue. 6.Reset Internet Explorer settings http://support.microsoft.com/kb/936213 For aditional details , instructions and methods to resolve the problem.refer: http://support.microsoft.com/kb/956196
